1. BASIC HASHMAP USAGE

---

import java.util.*;

class HashMapDemo {
public static void main(String[] args) {
HashMap<String, Integer> map = new HashMap<>();

```
    map.put("apple", 10);
    map.put("banana", 20);
    map.put("orange", 30);

    System.out.println(map.get("apple"));
    System.out.println(map.containsKey("banana"));

    map.remove("orange");

    System.out.println(map);
}
```

}

