2. FREQUENCY COUNT

---

import java.util.*;

class FrequencyCount {
public static void main(String[] args) {
int[] arr = {1, 2, 2, 3, 1, 4};

```
    HashMap<Integer, Integer> map = new HashMap<>();

    for (int num : arr) {
        map.put(num, map.getOrDefault(num, 0) + 1);
    }

    System.out.println(map);
}
```

}

